{"article_id":"oYSCZqSjCvpqZomD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The move could come as soon as Friday ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"sources said .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"|","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"AP , Reuters Photos","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Hill gets Obamacare fix","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Lawmakers and staff can breathe easy","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"- their health care tab is not going to soar next year .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The Office of Personnel Management , under heavy pressure from Capitol Hill , will issue a ruling","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that says","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"the government can continue to make a contribution to the health care premiums of members of Congress and their aides ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"according to several Hill sources .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"A White House official confirmed the deal","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"the proposed regulations will be issued next week .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Just Wednesday , reported","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that President Barack Obama told Democratic senators","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"that he was personally involved","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"in finding a solution .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"The problem was rooted in the original text of the Affordable Care Act .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Sen. Chuck Grassley","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"( R-Iowa )","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"inserted a provision","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"which said","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"members of Congress and their aides must be covered by plans","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"\" created \" by the law","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"or \" offered through an exchange. \"","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"Until now , OPM had not said","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"if the Federal Employee Health Benefits Program could contribute premium payments toward plans on the exchange .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"If payments stopped ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"lawmakers and aides would have faced thousands of dollars in additional premium payments each year .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Under the old system , the government contributed nearly 75 percent of premium payments .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Obama ' s involvement","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"in solving this impasse","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"was unusual ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to say the least .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"But it came","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"after serious griping from both sides of the aisle about the potential of a \" brain drain. \"","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"The fear ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"as told by sources in both parties ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"was that aides would head for more lucrative jobs ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"spooked by the potential","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"for spiking health premiums .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"There was a certain sense of urgency , too ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"since enrollment in the exchanges was set to begin Oct. 1 .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"There were discussions of a legislative fix","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"- attaching language to a must-pass bill","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"to fix the problem .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"But that would ' ve been too difficult in today ' s paralyzed Washington .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"White House officials acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"that a fix was needed .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"But they knew","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"once they dealt with it through a regulation ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"some Republicans would use it against them","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"- even though most of their party was privately obsessing over it .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"( D-Calif. ) ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"in a statement Thursday night , touted the law ' s benefits and Democrats ' efforts","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"to educate consumers .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" Members of Congress and their staffs must enroll in health marketplaces","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"as the Affordable Care Act requires , \"","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"she wrote .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"\" As we continue our work","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"to ensure the smooth implementation of this law","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"and look forward to the start of enrollment on October 1st ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"we will continue our efforts this August","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"to educate consumers on the law ' s provisions","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"and tout the critical benefits","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"already in place for millions of Americans . \"","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Anger was already evident as well .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"Senate Minority Whip John Cornyn","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"( R-Texas )","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"tweeted a link to ' s story Thursday night , with the comment :","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"\" Outrageous exemption for Congress . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":147,"left":75,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":76,"right":145,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":102,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":85,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":78,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":4,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":81,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":80,"right":10,"relation":"attributi